responsible of generating captions.\nOur GitHub repository can be found:\nhttps://github.com/elhagry1/SSL_ImageCaptioning_RotationPrediction\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 00:46:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-29"}
