e cluster where HST is confusion-limited. This precision is\ncomparable to measurements made by Gaia, HST and MUSE in the outer ~60\" of the\ncluster. This study is the first step towards building a science-driven\nastrometric error budget for an MCAO system and a prediction of what MAVIS\ncould do once on sky.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 07:14:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Aug 2021 04:46:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
