\ncritical points by proposed schemes and show that: the first scheme outperforms\naforementioned third-order WENO-Z improvements in terms of numerical\nresolution, while the second scheme indicates weak numerical robustness in\nspite of improved resolution and is mainly of theoretical significance\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 08:28:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-29"}
