 the cough detection camera detected coughing sounds with an F1\nscore of 90.0% (accuracy of 96.0%), and the cough location in the camera image\nwas tracked in real time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 10:44:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 17:01:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
